title: National Park Service Civil War data - Battle Positions
name: National Park Service Civil War data - Battle Positions
description: This dataset contains historical Battle Positions located in the National Park System.  The dataset was compiled (and edited) from a variety of sources including park-based GIS databases, park geo-referenced historical maps, GPS collection, U.S. Geological Survery 7.5' 1:24000 quadrangles and DOQQs.  The locations are in Latitude-Longitude (NAD83) decimal degrees.
